---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="關於 Linahhsheng。">
	<section class="about" aria-labelledby="page-title">
		<header>
			<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
			<h1 id="page-title">嗨，我是 Linahhsheng。</h1>
		</header>

		<div class="content">
			<p>這裡是一個留給自己的角落，我在這邊記錄我ㄉ笙活。</p>
			<p>寫下日常、羽球、音樂、遊戲、一些想法，還有慢慢長大的過程。</p>
			<p>希望藉由記錄生活，能更了解自己，還有這個世界。</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.about {
		width: min(100% - 3rem, 640px);
		padding: 5.5rem 0 6rem;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 0.875rem;
		color: #ff7575;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		letter-spacing: 0.04em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 7vw, 3.5rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		letter-spacing: -0.04em;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.content {
		margin-top: 3.5rem;
		color: #444444;
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		line-height: 2;
	}

	p {
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 480px) {
		.about {
			width: min(100% - 2rem, 640px);
			padding: 4rem 0;
		}
	}
</style>
